<br>
----------------------------<br>
<br>
Twas the night before “patch-day”, when all across the servers<br>
The players were waiting, to see the new berserkers<br>
The warriors were awaiting their new dps<br>
In hopes they’d gain respect, and be considered da’best!<br>
<br>
The knights were all learning to type LFG<br>
While shouting to the zone “pick me! pick me!”<br>
And Alan sat in his new leather chair<br>
Holding his nerf-bat, muttering “knights beware”<br>
<br>
When “You have been disconnected” showed on my screen<br>
I tried to log back in, but got 1017!<br>
Into Chat 31, I appeared like a flash<br>
People were screaming “this is what I get for my cash?!”<br>
<br>
The GMs were typing as if they were offended<br>
“Just give it a sec, its working as intended!”<br>
Eight hours later, I sat disbelieving<br>
What I saw on my screen, people were leaving!<br>
<br>
Back in the game I was sitting naked in PoK<br>
No armor, no weapons, not even a smock.<br>
/petition I did, along with the horde<br>
“We just killed Tunare and I lost my new sword!”<br>
<br>
“Server rollback, there’s nothing we can do”<br>
was the answer I received, from SoE employee_0012<br>
As I looted my corpse, I saw on the screen<br>
The message I feared – spelled out in green…<br>
<br>
*System_wide Message* Greetings Norrath!<br>
This is your God of hope, and sometimes of wrath!<br>
We have made some changes of a considerable amount,<br>
If you don’t like them, delete your account.<br>
<br>
“Now Warriors! now Rogues! now Rangers and Monks!<br>
You now have new powers that make knights look like punks!<br>
Now be good to those tanks that used to save your ass<br>
Their agro and usefulness has now come to pass.”<br>
<br>
SKs and Pallys – they used to tank so well<br>
But now they have been struck, with the nerf bat from hell.<br>
As Brael and the others, all sheathed up their swords<br>
Their guilds said “don’t worry – we’ll keep you aboard.”<br>
<br>
<br>
Surrounded by his staff of programming talents<br>
Alan shouted “Now that’s class-balance!”<br>
Petitions were pouring in; they were in for a fight<br>
“Merry Christmas to all, and to all a good knight!”<br>
<br>
Disclaimer – I was bored and wanted to poke some fun at SoE.  Most the events mentioned above are fictional and would never really happen. Any similarities to people or events are entirely coincidental. <br>
Copyright 2003 - Kaotix<br>
<br>
